name: Dimension Destroyer (Hanniee Tran, Eric S.)
description:
What would you do when you stumble upon a dimension door that let you travel to different realm? Where there are living beings and aliens that would try to attack you. You have roughly 3 minutes before you are able to use the dimension door again, can you survive?
